text: On May 1, 2017, Tax Exempt and Government Entities underwent a reorganization. The new Compliance, Planning & Classiﬁcation function absorbed several groups previously housed in Exempt Organizations Examination Planning and Review, and accepted ownership of this manual. The new IRM 4.70.6, TE/GE Examinations, Classiﬁcation & Case Assignment Procedures, supersedes this
